{"lemma":"ثَمَنِ","slug":"ثَمَنِ","root":"ث.م.ن","root_slug":"ث-م-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ث-م-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ثَمَن","root":"ثمن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":11},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4727","n4728","n4729","n4730"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a price","tags":["countable"],"examples":[{"text":"وَشَرَوْهُ بِثَمَنٍ بَخْسٍ دَرَاهِمَ مَعْدُودَةٍ","english":"And they sold him for cheap, [merely] a few pennies."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"an eighth","tags":["countable"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become valuable; to appreciate","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to set or fix the price of, to price; to try to assess the price or value of, to value; to evaluate; to appreciate","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to set or fix the price of, to price; to deem valuable, to value, to appreciate","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to divide into eight parts","tags":["transitive"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Ancient Greek τίμημα (tímēma), from τιμή (timḗ), from τῑ́ω (tī́ō), leveled to the root ث م ن (ṯ m n); ultimately from Proto-Indo-European *kʷey- (“value, honor”). Compare Classical Syriac ܛܝܼܡܵܐ (ṭīmā, “price, value”) and Jewish Literary Aramaic תמא (tmˀ, “duty, tax, fee”); for more see τιμή (timí) and τῑμάω (tīmáō).\n\nFrom the root ث م ن (ṯ m n); compare ثَمَانِيَة (ṯamāniya, “eight”)."},"ipa":["/θa.man/","/ta.man/","/θu.mun/","/θumn/","/tu.mun/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4727","headword_ar":"ثُمْنٌ","root":"vmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumunN","text_ar":"ثُمُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4728","headword_ar":"ثِمْنٌ","root":"vmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eighth young one"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offspring."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlv","text_ar":"ثلث"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One of the periods between two drinkings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waterings, of camels:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) [or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"end of one of those periods;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"night of coming to water which is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the eighth night of"},{"kind":"page_break","n":355},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a period between two drinkings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waterings, of camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"counting the night of the next preceding drinking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"watering, as the first:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riboEN","text_ar":"رِبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximosN","text_ar":"خِمْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] See also 4."}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n4729","headword_ar":"ثَمَنٌ","root":"vmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"price"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that the seller receives in return for the thing sold, whether money"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a commodity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaman","text_ar":"ثَمَن"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing sold: (S:) and also (Er-Rághib, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a compensation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substitute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, Er-Rághib, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whatever it be, for a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA,) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for a thing that is sold;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but in the sense commonly known,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as it is incumbent upon one to pay, of pieces of silver, and of gold"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or other money"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not commodities and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"value,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; (K;) its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiymap","text_ar":"قِيمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"estimated value,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by mutual consent, even though it be really excessive or deficient;"},{"kind":"text","text":"whereas the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiymap","text_ar":"قِيمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is its real value or worth, its equivalent: (MF:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avomaAnN","text_ar":"اَثْمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avomunN","text_ar":"اَثْمُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) the latter used only as a pl. of pauc., (Msb,) and [so]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avominapN","text_ar":"اَثْمِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (CK: not in the TA.) The saying in the Kur [ii. 38 and v. 48],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA ta$otaruwA biA=yaAtiY vamanFA qaliylFA","text_ar":"وَلَا تَشْتَرُوا بِا=يَاتِى ثَمَنًا قَلِيلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is metaphorical, meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And take ye not in exchange for my signs a small substitute:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. purchase not in exchange for belief in my word the happiness, or enjoyments, of the present life.] (Mgh.) With respect to this saying, Fr remarks, when"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamanFA","text_ar":"ثَمَنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in the Kur, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to the name of the thing sold or bought, in most cases it relates to two things whereof neither is a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vmn","text_ar":"ثمن"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense commonly known, i. e., such as pieces of gold and of silver: and such is the case when you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otarayotu vawobFA bikisaA='K","text_ar":"اِشْتَرَيْتُ ثَوْبًا بِكِسَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I purchased a garment with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ksA'","text_ar":"كساء"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]: either of these may be termed a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vmn","text_ar":"ثمن"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the other: but in speaking of pieces of silver and of gold, you prefix the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vmn","text_ar":"ثمن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[only]; as is done in [the chapter of] Yoosuf, [i. e. ch. xii., v. 20, where it is said,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa$arawohu bivamanK baxosK daraAhima maEoduwdapK","text_ar":"وَشَرَوْهُ بِثَمَنٍ بَخْسٍ دَرَاهِمَ مَعْدُودَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they sold him for a deficient,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an insufficient, price: for pieces of silver"},{"kind":"text","text":"not many, so as to require their being weighed, but few, and therefore"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"counted"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: for pieces of silver are always a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vmn","text_ar":"ثمن"},{"kind":"text","text":": and when you purchase pieces of silver and of gold with the like, you prefix the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"to whichever of the two you will, because each of them in this case is a purchase and a price. (T.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","T","MF","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n4730","headword_ar":"ثُمُنٌ","root":"vmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumonN","text_ar":"ثُمْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An eighth; an eighth part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamiynN","text_ar":"ثَمِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, * Mgh, Msb, K;) agreeably with a general rule applying to fractions, accord. to some; (M, K;) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valiyvN","text_ar":"ثَلِيثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"was ignored by AZ (T and S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlv","text_ar":"ثلث"},{"kind":"text","text":") and by others, (TA,) and so was"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamiysN","text_ar":"خَمِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlv","text_ar":"ثلث"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avomaAnN","text_ar":"اَثْمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}